            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿رَاضِيَةٖ﴾: مَرْضِيَّةٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "69:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عَالِيَةٖ﴾: مُرْتَفِعَةِ المكانِ والدَّرجَاتِ.</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "69:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿قُطُوفُهَا﴾: ثِمارُها.</h2>\n<h2>﴿دَانِيَةٞ﴾: قَرِيبَةُ التَّناوُلِ.</h2>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "69:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿هَنِيٓـَٔۢا﴾: أَكْلاً وشُرْباً يَهْنأُ بِهما صاحِبُهُما.</h2>\n<h2>﴿أَسۡلَفۡتُمۡ﴾: قدَّمْتُم.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ٱلۡأَيَّامِ ٱلۡخَالِيَةِ﴾: أَيَّامِ الدُّنيا الماضِيةِ.</h2>"
        },
