            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿حِسَابِيَهۡ﴾: جَزَائِي.</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "69:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿يَٰلَيۡتَهَا﴾: ياليتَ الموتَةَ الَّتِي مِتُّها في الدُّنيا.</p>\n<h2>﴿ٱلۡقَاضِيَةَ﴾: القاطِعةَ لِأَمْرِي فلا أُبْعَثُ.</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "69:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَآ أَغۡنَىٰ﴾: ما نَفَعَ.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "69:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿هَلَكَ﴾: غَابَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿سُلۡطَٰنِيَهۡ﴾: مُلْكِي.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "69:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَغُلُّوهُ﴾: اجْعَلُوا القَيْدَ في عُنُقِه.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "69:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿صَلُّوهُ﴾: أَدْخِلُوهُ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "69:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿سِلۡسِلَةٖ﴾: مَجْمُوعِ حَلَقٍ مِن حَدِيدٍ؛ دَاخِلٍ بَعْضُها فِي بَعْضٍ.</p>\n<h2>﴿ذَرۡعُهَا﴾: مِقْدَارُ طُولِهَا بالذِّراعِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَٱسۡلُكُوهُ﴾: فَأَدْخِلُوه في السِّلْسِلَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
