            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَلَا يَحُضُّ﴾: ولا يَحُثُّ.</h2>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "69:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿هَٰهُنَا﴾: يَومَ القِيامةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿حَمِيمٞ﴾: قَرِيبٌ يدفعُ عنْه العذابَ.</h2>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "69:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿غِسۡلِينٖ﴾: صَدِيدِ أَهْلِ النَّارِ، وما يَسِيلُ مِنْ أَجْسَادِهِم.</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "69:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱلۡخَٰطِـُٔونَ﴾: المُذْنِبُونَ أَشَدَّ الذَّنبِ؛ وهو الإِشْرَاكُ.</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "69:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿بِمَا تُبۡصِرُونَ﴾: مِنَ الأرضِ، والجِبالِ، والبِحارِ، والبَشَرِ، والسَّمواتِ، ونحوِها.</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "69:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمَا لَا تُبۡصِرُونَ﴾: مِنَ الأرواحِ، والملائِكةِ، وَأُمُورِ الآخِرَةِ.</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "69:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ﴾: يَنْطِقُ بِهِ مُحَمَّدٌ ﷺ، والكَلامُ كَلامُ المُرسِلِ سُبْحانَهُ وتَعَالَى.</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "69:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿قَلِيلٗا مَّا تُؤۡمِنُونَ﴾: تُؤْمِنُونَ إِيماناً قَلِيلاً لا يُنْجِيكُم مِن الخُلُود في النَّارِ.</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "69:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿قَلِيلٗا مَّا تَذَكَّرُونَ﴾: تَتَذَكَّرُونَ تَذَكُّراً قَلِيلاً.</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "69:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "69:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلَوۡ تَقَوَّلَ عَلَيۡنَا بَعۡضَ ٱلۡأَقَاوِيلِ﴾: وَلَو كَذَبَ عَلَينا بأنَّا قُلْنا قَوْلاً لم نَقُلْه.</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "69:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿لَأَخَذۡنَا مِنۡهُ بِٱلۡيَمِينِ﴾: لَأَخَذْناهُ بِقُوَّةٍ وقُدْرَةٍ.</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "69:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱلۡوَتِينَ﴾: هو عِرْقٌ عُلِّقَ به القلبُ، ويَسْقِي الجسدَ بالدَّمِ، فإذا قُطِعَ مات صاحِبُه.</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "69:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عَنۡهُ حَٰجِزِينَ﴾: يَمنعُونَ مِنْهُ عِقابَنا.</h2>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "69:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَتَذۡكِرَةٞ﴾: لَعِظَةٌ.</h2>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "69:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
